# 🌐 6️⃣ What is Eventual Consistency?

---

### Problem

Distributed systems have many servers.

Updates take time to reach all servers.

---

### Example

You update profile picture.

One server updates immediately.

Others update after a few seconds.

---

### Result

Temporary differences.

Eventually all become consistent.

---

### Why Companies Accept This

Higher scalability.

---

### Mental Model

News spreading across a city.

Everyone learns eventually.

---

# 🌐 7️⃣ Synchronous vs Asynchronous Communication

---

## Synchronous

Wait for response.

```text
Request
 ↓
Wait
 ↓
Response
```

---

### Example

Checking bank balance.

---

## Asynchronous

Do not wait.

```text
Request
 ↓
Continue working
```

Response later.

---

### Example

Sending email.

---

### Mental Model

Phone call vs voice message.

---

### Memory Trick

Synchronous = wait

Asynchronous = continue

---

